data.description: THE AVENUES OF CAYCE ! Step into the world of spacious elegance with this captivating 4 bedroom, 3 bathroom residence! Boasting over 2,150 square feet of luxurious living space, your family's dreams are ready to flourish within these walls. As you step through the door, unlock the boundless potential of this remarkable property, limited only by your imagination.  Nestled in a coveted neighborhood, this home harmoniously combines convenience with comfort, offering proximity to an array of shopping, dining, and entertainment venues. Don't let the opportunity of claiming this as your forever home pass you by.  Minutes from downtown Columbia SC. Reach out today to secure a private showing and explore the endless possibilities that await within these walls!
